Name: L-aminoadipate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase (NADH), mitochondrial Astrocyte
Reaction: L2aadp6sa[mA] + h2o[mA] + nad[mA] --> L2aadp[mA] + 2.0 h[mA] + nadh[mA]

Name: aldehyde dehydrogenase (acetylaldehyde, NAD), mitochondrial Astrocyte
Reaction: acald[mA] + h2o[mA] + nad[mA] --> ac[mA] + 2.0 h[mA] + nadh[mA]

Name: aspartate-glutamate mitochondrial shuttle Astrocyte
Reaction: asp-L[mA] + glu-L[cA] + h[cA] --> asp-L[cA] + glu-L[mA] + h[mA]

Name: glutamate dehydrogenase (NADP), mitochondrial Astrocyte
Reaction: glu-L[mA] + h2o[mA] + nadp[mA] --> akg[mA] + h[mA] + nadph[mA] + nh4[mA]

Name: lactaldehyde dehydrogenase, mitochondrial Astrocyte
Reaction: h2o[mA] + lald-D[mA] + nad[mA] --> 2.0 h[mA] + lac-D[mA] + nadh[mA]

Name: Cytochrome P450 11A1, mitochondrial [Precursor] Astrocyte
Reaction: chsterol[mA] + h[mA] + nadph[mA] + 2.0 o2[mA] --> 4mptnl[mA] + 2.0 h2o[mA] + nadp[mA] + prgnlone[mA]

Name: pyruvate carboxylase Astrocyte
Reaction: atp[mA] + hco3[mA] + pyr[mA] --> adp[mA] + h[mA] + oaa[mA] + pi[mA]

Name: succinate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase (NAD) reversible (mitochondrial) Astrocyte
Reaction: h2o[mA] + nad[mA] + sucsal[mA] --> 2.0 h[mA] + nadh[mA] + succ[mA]

Name: aspartate-glutamate mitochondrial shuttle Neuron
Reaction: asp-L[mN] + glu-L[cN] + h[cN] --> asp-L[cN] + glu-L[mN] + h[mN]

Name: citrate synthase Neuron
Reaction: accoa[mN] + h2o[mN] + oaa[mN] --> cit[mN] + coa[mN] + h[mN]

Name: glutamate dehydrogenase (NADP), mitochondrial Neuron
Reaction: glu-L[mN] + h2o[mN] + nadp[mN] --> akg[mN] + h[mN] + nadph[mN] + nh4[mN]

Name: L-glutamate reversible transport via proton symport, mitochondrial Neuron
Hydroxymethylglutaryl CoA synthase (ir) Neuron
Reaction: aacoa[mN] + accoa[mN] + h2o[mN] --> coa[mN] + h[mN] + hmgcoa[mN]

Name: Cytochrome P450 11A1, mitochondrial [Precursor] Neuron
Reaction: chsterol[mN] + h[mN] + nadph[mN] + 2.0 o2[mN] --> 4mptnl[mN] + 2.0 h2o[mN] + nadp[mN] + prgnlone[mN]

Name: pyruvate mitochondrial transport via proton symport Neuron
NAD(P) transhydrogenase Neuron
Reaction: h[cN] + nadh[mN] + nadp[mN] <=> h[mN] + nad[mN] + nadph[mN]
